Class CommunityFinder

java.lang.Object
  java.util.Observable
      org.cougaar.core.qos.ca.CommunityFinder
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
CommunityFinder.ForAgent, CommunityFinder.ForAny
public abstract class CommunityFinder
extends java.util.Observable
implements CommunityResponseListener, CommunityChangeListener

This utility class helps simplify Community lookup. For now it comes in two variants, which are inner class extensions.

Nested Class Summary
static class CommunityFinder.ForAgent
          This variant of CommunityFinder is useful for finding Communities of which a given Agent is a member.
static class CommunityFinder.ForAny
          This variant of CommunityFinder is useful for finding Communities without assuming any particular Agent is a member.
